Products.RichDescription:
Protein for power to the muscles 
Fibre for a happy gut 
As part of a healthy balanced diet.

What's inside matters
Macro Organic Buckwheat Flour is made from whole grain buckwheat with no nasties.
Use buckwheat flour to make delicious pancakes with a slight nutty flavour. You can add it to almost any recipe that calls for regular flour.

One 50g serve of Macro Organic Buckwheat Flour contributes more than 100% of the 48g whole grain Daily Target Intake.
